== About ==

LinkedWiki is a Mediawiki extension.
* In your wiki, you can test your Sparql Queries via the special pages.
* In a wiki page, you can insert the result of a query sparql.
* In a module/infobox (via Lua), you can reuse your RDF data.
* You can also build a Mediawiki widget with your data.

See the doc : http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:LinkedWiki

