== Installation ==

Put this line in your Localsettings.php for the parser "sparql" and the special pages :

    wfLoadExtension( 'LinkedWiki' );

Optional extensions :
* "Scribunto" in order to use the Lua class of Linkedwiki
* "Widgets"  in order to use the parser WSparql with a Mediawiki widget

== Tutorial and download ==

See : http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:LinkedWiki

